name: F.A.R.M. (Canceled)
blurb: Picture Back At the Barnyard meets Call of Duty.  Play as humanized animals who work for an underground military organization, F.A.R.M.

rewards.reward: No Reward
Our eternal gratitude...Want to help but don't want any of the special items?  Every little bit helps, and we are eternally grateful to all of our backers, no matter the size of the donation.

Skunk Bumper sticker...Bumper Sticker featuring a character from the game.  Choose between the skunk information officer, duck bomber, goose pilot, Spider spy, or Officer Swinehaur.  Also receive access to the developer blog, exclusive to backers.
Just the game..A digital copy of the game will be sent to you via email upon release of the game.  Also receive access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.

F.A.R.M. Coffee Mug...A coffee mug with the logo and characters printed on it and a digital copy of the game.  (Mug will ship once the campaign ends.  Game will be delivered via email once it is released).  Also receive access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.

F.A.R.M. Mousepad...Get a mousepad with the F.A.R.M. character montage and a copy of the game.  (Mousepad will be shipped after the campaign ends.  Games will be received via email after the production is completed).  Also receive acces to the developer blog exclusive to backers.

F.A.R.M. Cap...Baseball cap with logo printed on it, a digital copy of the game, your name listed in the credits as a Bronze Backer, and access to the developer blog, exclusive to backers.  Hats will be shipped after campaign ends.  Game will be delivered via email upon release.

F.A.R.M. T-Shirt...A short-sleeved tee with the logo and characters printed on it, a digital copy of the game, your name listed in the credits as a Bronze Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  Tees will be shipped after campaign ends.  Game will be delivered via email upon release.

F.A.R.M. Calendar...A 12-month 2014 calendar, featuring concept and screenshot art from the game, your name listed in the credits as a Bronze Backer, a digital copy of the game, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (Calendar will be shipped after campaign ends.  Game will be delivered via email upon release.

Digital Artbook...Digital artbook featuring concept art and screenshots from the game.  Also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Silver Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (Artbook will be delivered via email after campaign ends.  Game will be delivered via email upon release).

Design a gadget...Work with our team to design a gadget or tool that will be available in the game.  (Restrictions apply, must be considered PG rated items).  Also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits under Bronze Backers, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.

Ouya package...The game will be exclusive to the Ouya console initially.  Be the first to play it!  Receive an Ouya console, a copy of the digital artbook, a copy of the game, your name listed in the credits as a Silver Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (Console will be shipped after campaign ends.  Game code will be delivered via email upon release).

30 Second ads...Have your company advertisement placed on a scrolling billboard.  Ads will rotate every 30 seconds, constantly scrolling through each ad, Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name and/or company name in the credits as a Silver backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (Ads must be PG or better).  You will be contacted by a member of our team after campaign ends to discuss ad.

Your name or face in graffiti...Have your name or face painted on the side of a building somewhere in the game world.  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Silver Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.

Become a criminal...Have your image placed on a wanted poster which will be scattered around the game world.  Also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Silver backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted by a member of our team after campaign ends to give us a photo you would like used.  Restrictions apply.  Must be rated PG or better.  Game will be delivered via email upon release).

Personalized Easter egg...Have an Easter egg designed specifically for you in the form of a mini-game within the game world.  You will have exclusive access to this mini game by way of a unique code given only to you.  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits under Gold Backers, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.

Poster ad...Advertise your company or products on a poster to be seen within the game world.  This will be permanent advertising within the game.  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name or company name in the credits as a Gold Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after the campaign ends to discuss your ad).

One-of-a-kind artwork...Receive a one-of-a-kind piece of art drawn by our concept artist, John Easling.  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (Artwork will be delivered after the campaign ends.  Game will be delivered via email upon release).

Advertise on a vehicle...Place your company or product ad on the side of a bus or bus stop.  (Restrictions apply.  Ads must be rated PG or better).  Backers who choose this reward will receive a digital copy of the game, your name or your company's name in the credits under Gold Backers, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after the campaign ends to discuss your ad).

Name an EMT...Help personalize the game by naming one of the EMTs who rescue the wounded in battle.  (Restrictions apply.  Must be PG rated or better).  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer and Additional Designer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after the campaign ends to discuss your name ideas).

Your name in a headline of the newspaper...Have your name printed in a headline of the newspaper within the game world.  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits under Gold Backers, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.

Static billboard...Have a full-sized billboard ad in the game.  Permanent advertising for your business or company placed on a billboard in the game world.  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name or company name in the credits as a Gold Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after the campaign ends to discuss your ad).

Name a building...Help personalize our game by naming one of the buildings in the world.  (Restrictions apply.  Must be PG rated or better).  Backers who choose this reward will receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer as well as listed under Additional Designers, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after campaign ends to discuss your name ideas).

Name a street...Help personalize the game by naming one of the streets in the game world.  (Restrictions apply.  Must be PG rated or better).  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer and under Additional Designers, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after the campaign ends to discuss your name ideas).

3D yourself...Have a 3D model of yourself created by our art team to be used as an npc within the game.  You can be IN the game for the whole world to see.  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after campaign ends to get us your photo so we can turn it into a 3D model).

Ad on a marquee...Advertise your company or products on the movie theater marquee.  This is permanent advertising within the game world.  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name or company name in the credits as a Gold Backer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after the campaign ends to discuss your ad).

Design a mission...Work with our level design team to design a side mission in the game.  Backers who choose this reward will receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer as well as listed under Additional Designers, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.

Name the ship...Help us personalize the game by naming the enemy battleship.  (Restrictions apply.  Must be PG rated or better).  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer and Additional Designer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after campaign ends to discuss your name ideas).

Name the Ranch...You name the ranch that holds the F.A.R.M. headquarters (restrictions apply.  Must be PG rated or better).  Backers who choose this reward will also receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer as well as listed under Additional Designers, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after the campaign ends to discuss your name ideas).

Name the boss...Name the enemy boss after yourself or give him a name of your choosing.  (Restrictions apply.  Must be PG rated or better).  Backers who choose this reward will receive a digital copy of the game, your name in the credits as a Gold Backer and Additional Designer, and access to the developer blog exclusive to backers.  (You will be contacted after the campaign ends to discuss your name ideas).
